ies, Studies in International Security and Arms Control, sponsored by the Center for International Security and Arms Control at Stanford University.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / International Relations / General.2bisacsh1 aLewis, John W., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aXue, Litai, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertStanford University Press Archive eBook-Package Pre-2000z978311070421140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362211140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503622111423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503622111/original  a978-3-11-070421-1  Stanford University Press Archive eBook-Package Pre-2000b2000  aGBV-deGruyter-alles